Sells prepaid virtual gift cards in exchange for Bitcoins.

The brands of gift cards cards offered, also referred to as prepaid debit cards, are:

* Amazon
* NewEgg
* Wal-Mart

The price offered on BTC Buy reflects ~5% surcharge. However, the site offers fast turnaround, with most orders filled within less than an hour, which makes it attractive to those who want to spend BTC without wait.

##History

The site was launched on June 8, 2011 (2.1).
